Vendored verbatim from https://github.com/Berlin-Institute-of-Health/Genkidata
opts/Blutdruck.opt — the openEHR "Blutdruck" (GECCO / NUM) Operational Template
(ADL 1.4 OPT, generated by the Ocean OPT Generator). Copyright Berlin Institute of
Health; licensed Apache-2.0. Vendored here so the openEHR validator-zoo lane can load
the OPT and confirm that blood_pressure.source.json and blood_pressure.augmented.json
both validate under it — the empirical half of the in-band-complement claim.
